translations: [动][植] 二态的；[晶体] 双晶的

sentences.sentence: Both types of rice embryos have dimorphic cotyledons.
sentences.translation: 第一类型与第二类型稻胚都具有二型子叶。

sentences.sentence: Firstly, our results indicated that the monomorphic populations of L. pinceana were originated from adjacent western dimorphic populations.
sentences.translation: 首先，研究结果表明滇丁香长花柱型单态居群起源于西部邻近的二态居群。
